meta {
  name: Activate a custom telephony provider
  type: http
  seq: 6
}

post {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/api/v1/telephony-providers/{{customTelephonyProviderId}}/lifecycle/activate
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Activates a custom telephony provider by its ID. You must activate a provider before it can be used.

**Responses:**
- `200`: OK
- `403`: 
- `404`:
}
